Zoey was nursing when OS arrived. MOB held her cradled in her arms. Zoey is having 3-5 bowel movements each day along with several wet diapers. MOB used OS's scale to weigh the baby. Zoey had a weight gain. MOB reports that Zoey is staying awake longer during the day. She is doing tummy time each day and loves it according to MOB. Zoey when awake was pink and alert at today's visit.
OS Jeanine DeLong
